ga a Movistar+ el 18 de enero|work=[[El Peri\u00f3dico de Catalunya]]|language=Spanish|date=22 November 2018}}</ref> Season 2, consisting of 8 episodes, was released on 17 January 2020.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.larazon.es/television/20191029/cdgtmi5nhvblpmi54ipd764kzq.html|title=\u00abEl Embarcadero\u00bb vuelve en enero de 2020|work=larazon.es|language=Spanish|date=29 October 2019 |access-date=30 October 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Premise==\nAlejandra ([[Ver\u00f3nica S\u00e1nchez]]) is a high-profile architect in Valencia who is shattered by the secrets left behind by the death of Oscar, her husband of 15 years. She discovers he was leading a double-life with another woman, Veronica, in a nearby village, Albufera. She decides to approach the woman under another identity to discover why her husband lived a lie and what really happened on the fateful night of his death.\n\n==Cast==\n* [[\u00c1lvaro Morte]] as \u00d3scar\n* [[Ver\u00f3nica S\u00e1nchez]] as Alejandra\n* Irene Arcos as Ver\u00f3nica\n* Roberto Enr\u00edquez as Conrado\n* Marta Milans as Katia\n* Judit Ampudia as Ada\n* [[Antonio Garrido (actor)|Antonio Garrido]] as Big Boss\n* Miquel Fern\u00e1ndez as Fran\n* Paco Manzanedo as Vicent\n* '''with''' [[Cecilia Roth]] as Blanca\n\n==Episodes==\n=== Season 1===\n{{Episode table |total_width=74 |background= #2ECCFA |overall= |title=  |titleR=  |director=  |airdate= |country= |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 1\n |Title = Episodio 1\n |DirectedBy = Jes\u00fas Colmenar\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|01|18}}\n |ShortSummary = Alejandra is a successful architect in Valencia and is in a loving marriage to Oscar, who goes to Frankfurt every week for work. Her whole world comes crashing down when she gets a phone call from Lieutenant Conrado that Oscar's body was found in a nearby lagoon town, Albufera. Devastated and confused, she seeks answers and finds out that Oscar had a whole other life in Albufera. Moreover, she discovers from the videos on